{* Confirmation of GeoCode and reType Membership  *}
<div class="crm-block crm-form-block crm-contact-task-delete-form-block">
<div class="messages status no-popup">
  <div class="icon inform-icon"></div>
  You have selected <strong>{$totalSelectedContacts}</strong> Contacts.
</div>
  <p>Clicking 'GeoCode and reType BCNDP Membership' will: <br/>
     <ul><li>grab a Contact's Primary address</li>
     <li>sends latitude and longitude (or Postal Code if lat/lon not available) to OpenNorth API to determine the Constituency - Primary and the Riding - Primary</li>
     <li>for ALL these Contacts</li>
     <li>and will then reType their Membership to General-Constituency</li>
     <li>in case there is an override == 1 we'll use the Constituency - Transferred to Constituency</li>
     <li><strong>This action cannot be undone!</strong></li>
    <ul>
  </p>
  <div class="crm-submit-buttons">{include file="CRM/common/formButtons.tpl"}</div>
</div>
